{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I worked in that [? steinbrook. ?] In [? the steinbrook, ?] we'd have to go out of the camp with the guards, the SS.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was about a half a mile, a mile away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- [? one ?] SS, and mostly what they used SS in those camps-- they were injured on the front or something, and they had to give them something to keep busy so they send those to death camps.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you imagine those who were injured a little bit that the one-- one SS were screaming like terrible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when you hear the screaming, gave me a feeling like terribly he felt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like you could get a gun out and kill you-- anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- I can not believe how I survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried to-- when we saw the kitchen, grab potatoes, getting-- stealing from the kitchen some to help yourself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember one thing that happened in Blizyn, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got sick-- typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- and they put you into a barrack special for the sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't know how I got-- some people, a lot of people died from sickness, and I got out about a week later.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got out of this, because if you were there, you know they're not gonna survive because they're going to kill right away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I got-- felt better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after typhus, I was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could climb up a [? pole, ?] if you were hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what I did, I-- I took from the kitchen with-- they bring in potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stole a few potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what happened-- and I went in-- it was a-- like a something, empty building.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
